{"code":0,"data":[{"cid":585872,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":121907,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"即使没有树洞，也会在其他平台比如知乎上被传播吧？","timestamp":1605844699,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":585879,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Bob","permissions":["report"],"pid":121907,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"为什么要被关？","timestamp":1605844729,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":585881,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Carol","permissions":["report"],"pid":121907,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"是谁说会被关的？","timestamp":1605844754,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":585891,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":121907,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"传播的深层原因是这个事件的各种标签都触及了社会的撕裂面，比如高等教育/清华，艺术生，性别对立，身高歧视，这些和树洞没有任何关系，树洞有或没有都会照样存在","timestamp":1605844805,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":585896,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Dave","permissions":["report"],"pid":121907,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"微博天天出瓜，微博被关掉了吗😅","timestamp":1605844833,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":585897,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":121907,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"希望树洞好好的活下去","timestamp":1605844843,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":585931,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Eve","permissions":["report"],"pid":121907,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Alice: +1","timestamp":1605845001,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":585996,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Francis","permissions":["report"],"pid":121907,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re Dave: 微博的目的可能就是出瓜，但树洞只是我们学生匿名聊天的地方啊","timestamp":1605845302,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":586223,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Grace","permissions":["report"],"pid":121907,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"没有树洞就直接上乎了，我倒觉得整个事件中树洞是这些平台里最理智最可控的一个。","timestamp":1605846573,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":586301,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":121907,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"我不赞同没有树洞就能直接上乎，尽管知乎是清华bbs，但这件事在经过树洞反复发酵放大之前远远没有达到上乎的讨论度。","timestamp":1605846955,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":586328,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":true,"name":"洞主","permissions":["report"],"pid":121907,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"美院女生发的朋友圈，最多也就能影响数百人，哪怕反转了。","timestamp":1605847113,"type":"text","url":""},{"cid":587224,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"is_dz":false,"name":"Alice","permissions":["report"],"pid":121907,"reply_to":-1,"tag":null,"text":"Re 洞主: 你还是对朋友圈舆论的理解不够深入。之前朋友圈p大点事上乎的多了去了。这次的事件集中了这么多爆点，闹大是必然的。","timestamp":1605852726,"type":"text","url":""}],"post":{"attention":false,"deleted":false,"image_metadata":{},"likenum":5,"permissions":["report","fold"],"pid":121907,"reply":12,"tag":null,"text":"经此一事，树洞可能要被关停了吧。\n回顾整件事的发展，男生社死是先在树洞放大的，发转以后也是树洞追着要公开女生信息的，上知乎、豆瓣乃至微博，源头也是树洞。\n说实话我不愿意见到树洞关掉，尽管它放大了很多丑恶，但在这之外也有很多让我珍惜的东西，我可以在这里获得更多课程、社工乃至保研相关的信息，也能遇到一些平时遇不到的有共同兴趣爱好的人，在深夜睡不着的时候也能得到陌生人的关心和陪伴，无聊的时候还能在这玩玩飞花令。\n但这些，可能在明天，也许在今天，就要消失了吧。\n最后，我想祝愿在树洞里也保留最大善意的人们将来也能接受到更多的善意，在树洞里发泄自己的戾气的人们早日遭到反噬。","timestamp":1605844636,"type":"text","updated_at":1606782653,"url":"","vote":{}}}